---
---

<div class="welcome-container">
  <div class="welcome-card">
    <h1>Welcome to docs</h1>
    <p class="intro-lead">Documenting everything so future me stops asking <b>ChatGPT</b> the same question twice.</p>
    <p class="intro-sub">Well… not everything. Only the topics I actually care enough to revisit. If I had to ask twice, it deserves a blog post.</p>
    
    <div class="features-section">
      <h3 class="features-heading">Features</h3>
      <div class="features-grid">
        <div class="feature-card">
          <i class="fa-solid fa-code feature-icon"></i>
          <strong>Syntax Highlighting</strong>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-card">
          <i class="fa-solid fa-copy feature-icon"></i>
          <strong>One-click Copy</strong>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-card">
          <i class="fa-solid fa-magnifying-glass feature-icon"></i>
          <strong>Live Search</strong>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-card">
          <i class="fa-solid fa-bars-progress feature-icon"></i>
          <strong>Reading Progress</strong>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-card">
          <i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-right-arrow-left feature-icon"></i>
          <strong>Width Toggle</strong>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-card">
          <i class="fa-solid fa-text-height feature-icon"></i>
          <strong>Font Size Control</strong>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-card">
          <i class="fa-solid fa-moon feature-icon"></i>
          <strong>Dark & Light Mode</strong>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-card">
          <i class="fa-solid fa-chevron-left feature-icon"></i>
          <strong>Prev / Next Navigation</strong>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="ai-disclaimer">
      <i class="fa-solid fa-robot ai-disclaimer-icon"></i>
      <p>All content researched with AI. I asked the questions. It answered. We both pretended to be sure.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<style>
  .welcome-container {
    max-width: var(--reading-max-width);
    width: 100%;
    margin-top: 2rem;
    padding-bottom: 4rem;
  }

  .welcome-card {
    padding: 2.5rem 0 1.5rem 0;
  }

  .welcome-card h1 {
    font-family: var(--font-interface);
    font-size: 2.85rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.15;
    color: var(--text-active);
    letter-spacing: -0.03em;
  }

  .welcome-card .intro-lead {
    color: var(--text-main);
    font-family: var(--font-reading);
    font-size: 1.35rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
    font-weight: 400;
  }

  .welcome-card .intro-lead b {
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--accent);
  }

  .welcome-card .intro-sub {
    color: var(--text-muted);
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
  }

  .features-section {
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border-color);
    padding-top: 2.5rem;
    margin-top: 1rem;
  }

  .features-heading {
    font-size: 0.72rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .features-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(220px, 1fr));
    gap: 1rem;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .feature-card {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.875rem;
    padding: 1.1rem 1.25rem;
    border-radius: 12px;
    border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
    background-color: var(--bg-card);
    transition: border-color 0.25s ease, background-color 0.25s ease, transform 0.25s ease, box-shadow 0.25s ease;
    user-select: none;
  }

  .feature-card:hover {
    border-color: var(--accent);
    background-color: var(--accent-glow);
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    box-shadow: 0 6px 16px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.03);
  }

  html.dark-mode .feature-card:hover {
    box-shadow: 0 6px 16px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
  }

  .feature-icon {
    color: var(--accent);
    font-size: 1.15rem;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    width: 24px;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .feature-card strong {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--text-active);
  }

  .ai-disclaimer {
    margin-top: 2.5rem;
    padding: 1.25rem 1.5rem;
    border-radius: 10px;
    border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--bg-card) 0%, var(--bg-hover) 100%);
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.4rem;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .ai-disclaimer::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    top: 0;
    bottom: 0;
    width: 3px;
    background: var(--accent);
    border-radius: 3px 0 0 3px;
  }

  .ai-disclaimer-icon {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    color: var(--accent);
    margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
  }

  .ai-disclaimer p {
    font-family: var(--font-reading);
    font-size: 0.975rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin: 0;
    font-style: italic;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .welcome-card h1 {
      font-size: 2.2rem;
    }
    .features-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>
